<p><a target="_blank" href="http://wayward.wikidot.com/">The Wayward Society</a>.</p>
<blockquote>
<p>The Wayward Society is a volunteer organization dedicated to the eradication and investigation of dangerous, paranormal, and otherwise anomalous entities. Here, you will find documentation on the findings of those who have risked their lives or sacrificed themselves for this goal.</p>
</blockquote>
<p>Its creed and mission is kinda similar to our Wiki, but unlike others it's not directly derived from SCPF (at least inspired by it, say).</p>
<hr />
<p>Personal perspective: WwdS is more &quot;classical&quot; and gives an undertone of early-modern mystical, uncanny fantasies and while Foundation relies more on modern sci &amp; tech and resembles hardcore sci-fi.</p>

							</div>

